cs|1|At|^-{ There is no way to sign off in 2@C or 2@D after a 1NT opening in the SAYC bidding system, 
 but it is possible to sign off in 3@C or 3@D. To do this, respond 2@S to your partner's 1NT. }
^-
|
pg| ***** 85 ***** |


cs|3|at|^-{ When Jacoby transfers are being used, the 2@S response to 1NT is ^*Ifreed up^*N since it is no
 longer needed as a natural bid. SAYC uses the 2@S response to sign off in 3@C or 3@D. }
^-|
