 The opener has already described his hand - he should respect his partner's judgment! }

|
pg| ***** 91 ***** |


cs|3|at|{ 2. In the SAYC bidding system the responder can bid 3@C or 3@D directly over 
 1NT to describe a hand with invitational strength and a long, strong minor suit. }
^-
